{
  "id": "adv_main_01_01_00",
  "title": "星見編1章1話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_shed-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（それは突然の告白だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It was all in a sudden.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re going to be an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "うん\nまだ、なれると決まった訳じゃないんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nThough it’s not official yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり変だよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You probably think it’s weird‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや……そういう訳じゃないけど\nただ、意外だなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Weird? Not really.\nI’m just… surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.600000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_street-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 18.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（長瀬麻奈とは高校二年で初めてクラスメイトになった）\n（隣の席ではあったが、特に仲が良かった訳ではない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana Nagase and I became classmates in our second year of high school.）\n（We weren’t exactly friends. We just sat next to each other.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（元々、明るくて美人な彼女はクラスでも人気があって）\n（どらちかというと日陰組の俺からは遠い存在だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana was bright and beautiful—the popular girl in class.）\n（Meanwhile‚ I tended to avoid the spotlight. We were worlds apart.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.90143585205078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（授業中、たまに視界に入る彼女の横顔の美しさに）\n（ドキリとすることはあったが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sometimes‚ during class‚ I’d catch a glimpse of her beautiful face‚）\n（and my heart would skip a beat.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（それはグラビアアイドルを見るのと変わりはない――）\n（ただ遠くから眺めるだけの可愛い子でしかなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But…It felt no different than looking at a gravure idol in a magazine.）\n（All she ever was to me was a pretty girl out of my league.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（なのに……麻奈から突然）\n（話があるから残って欲しいと言われた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Until one day‚ in a sudden‚）\n（she asked me if we could talk after school.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（ドキドキする心臓に、どうせ大した用事じゃない）\n（期待は禁物、と言い聞かせながら臨んだ放課後）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（My heart raced as I waited for her.）\n（I told myself not to get my hopes up‚ that it was probably nothing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_park-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 68.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それ……みんなは知ってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… Does everyone know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。誰にも言ってないから\nうまくいかなかったら恥ずかしいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I haven't told anyone.\nIt would be embarrassing if things didn't go well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（――いや、待て）\n（もしかしたらドッキリかもしれない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait a minute――）\n（This might be a prank.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（クラスメイトがどこかに隠れていて笑いながら）\n（この状況を楽しんでいるのではないか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Our classmates are probably hiding somewhere right now‚）\n（holding in their laughter at this whole situation.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "ドッキリとかじゃないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a prank‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんに、お願いがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a favor to ask you‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha… what is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "あのね……クラスで一番、私と普通に\n接してくれる男子って誰なのかな……って考えたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I was thinking…\nNone of the boys in class treat me normally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな私と話す時は、変にかしこまるっていうか\n他の女子と話す時とは違うっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They all act so awkward and formal around me‚\nbut they’re not like that around the other girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "そう考えたら、ああ\n{user}くんは普通だなあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I realized there was one exception.\nYou‚ {user}. You’ve always acted normal‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "だから……お願いしようと思って……あ、でも\nとてもワガママでメチャクチャなお願いだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So…I thought you could help me and…\nOh‚ well‚ it’s a crazy and selfish request.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "嫌だったら、嫌って言って\n私もダメ元でお願いするんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don’t like the idea‚ just turn me down.\nI’m asking you this fully expecting to be rejected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A―ah……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "ええとね…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…um……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（それから、二年が経った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And two years have passed since then.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_studio-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 137.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（その告白は、俺が心のどこかで期待していた内容では）\n（――もちろんなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That confession‚ it wasn't what I secretly hoped for）\n（――Of course‚ totally different.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしても不安だから、一緒に地元の芸能事務所）\n（星見プロダクションに入ってくれないか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She asked me to work with her at Hoshimi Productions‚ a local talent agency）\n（because she was anxious about going on her own.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "（そして、そのフラットな目線で助言してくれないか）\n（聞いた時、あまりに無茶苦茶な頼みに笑ってしまった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And asked if I could give her advice with my unbiased perspective.）\n（I couldn’t help laughing. The whole thing sounded so ridiculous.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "（けど、なぜか俺は麻奈の頼みを聞き入れ）\n（アルバイトとして星見プロダクションに入ったのだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But for some reason‚ I accepted Mana’s request）\n（and started as a part―timer at Hoshimi Productions.）",
        "id": ""
      },
