      "text": "（麻奈は階段を駆け上がるように人気者になり）\n（卒業式には記念写真の列で大変だったのを覚えている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana rapidly ascended the ladder of stardom‚）\n（becoming so popular that classmates queued to take pictures with her at graduation.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、分かった\nまだ時間はあるから慌てないようにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. I understand.\nDon’t rush. You’ve got plenty of time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
