      "text": "うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ok.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh023.m4a",
      "text": "（故障で止まった鉄道を降り、タクシーで会場に）\n（向かう……そう言ってきた麻奈に俺は電話で答える）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Getting off the stopped train due to a malfunction‚ heading to the venue by taxi…）\n（That's what Mana said over the phone‚ and I replied.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh024.m4a",
      "text": "（全てのアイドルにランキング制度）\n（「VENUSプログラム」が導入され）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（All idols）\n（are ranked through the \"VENUS Program\"）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh025.m4a",
      "text": "（ライブバトルによって）\n（ランキングが決定するようになって十数年）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The rankings are determined by live battles‚）\n（and the program have established a little over a decade ago.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh026.m4a",
      "text": "（新人アイドルの頂点を決める大会）\n（NEXT VENUSグランプリ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And there is a tournament to determine the top new idol‚）\n（The NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
