      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_00-koh028.m4a",
      "text": "（今日、その頂点に立つ者が決まる）\n（麻奈はその最有力候補と言われていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The one who stands at the top will be decided today.）\n（Mana was said to be the top contender for that.）",
