      "text": "（正直、麻奈の願いを聞いて事務所に入った時は）\n（恐らく半年程度で辞めることになると思っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Truth be told‚ when I first took this job at Mana‘s request‚）\n（I figured I‘d quit within a few months.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
