      "text": "（だが、まさかここまで来るとは）\n（卒業の時、麻奈は俺に事務所を辞めるように言った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I had no idea we’d make it that far.）\n（At graduation‚ Mana encouraged me to quit Hoshimi Productions.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
