      "text": "（この仕事の面白さを感じ始めていたし）\n（何より麻奈がどこまで行くのか見届けたかったのだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In part‚ because I’d actually become fond of the job.）\n（But honestly‚ I wanted to be with Mana and see how far she‘d go.）",
        "id": ""
