      "text": "（決勝は後日改めてという形にはならないだろうか）\n（頭に浮かぶのはそんなことばかりだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Will they reschedule the finals for another day?）\n（Those were the only thoughts going through my mind.）",
